last_episode_to_air.overview: An Arkansas man with his own security firm is found dead on a deserted road, leaving behind his daughter to pick up the pieces; 13 years later, the victim's daughter finds clues when another murder occurs.

name: My Murder Story
overview: A look at those left in the wake of a murder as they dig for the truth among the unexpected and unnerving secrets of the murdered loved ones.
